{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·001.1", "text_original": "雞既鳴矣，朝既盈矣。匪雞則鳴，蒼蠅之聲。", "text_normalized": "雞既鳴矣，朝既盈矣。匪雞則鳴，蒼蠅之聲。", "notes": "雞鳴 Chinese stanza 1."}
